title: Tiddler Link Demo
caption: Tiddler Link
tags: TableOfContents [[Simple Outline Demo]]
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Demonstrates the `tiddler-link` attribute.  Each tiddler item gets a small ✳ link on the right side of its row.  Clicking the ✳ opens the tiddler in the story river without toggling the outline node — so you can read entries without losing your place in the outline.

Also uses `open-depth="1"` (added in 0.7.0) to pre-open the top level on the first visit.

<$simple-outline class="outline" tiddler-link="yes" open-depth="1" text="""
